233	/// End-to-end resume: first run fails at `push-app` (simulated
234	/// by passing a bogus bookmark that jj accepts but the bare-git
235	/// remote rejects on push). Second run with `--from push-app`
236	/// and the correct bookmark completes the flow. Confirms state
237	/// persists across invocations and `--from` overrides the
